headline: 3 Reasons SBUX is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since July 2025, Starbucks has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 4.9% while floating around $88.82. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 10.4% gain during that period.
